#encoding: utf-8

Feature: Literals8 - Maps

  Scenario: [1] Return an empty map
    Given any graph
    When executing query:
      """
      RETURN {} AS literal
      """
    Then the result should be, in any order:
      | literal |
      | {}      |
    And no side effects

